name: Plectix Biosystems
overview: Plectix BioSystems, Inc. engages in the research and development of approaches to the protein transformations and interactions that underpin cellular signaling networks. The company offers Cellucidate, a Web-based platform and language system that helps academic and drug-discovery researchers to represent pathways and study cell signaling systems, as well as develops approaches for drug discovery and development. Its approaches enable biologists to develop signaling processes and design interventions based on molecular mechanisms. The company was founded in 2004 and is based in Somerville, Massachusetts.
